WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.268
I saw weapons that the United States has never used before.

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:08.520
They are about to use them.

00:00:27.291 --> 00:00:27.680
They are going to use weapons that our country has never used before in battle.

00:00:27.680 --> 00:00:35.200
Maybe we've practiced with them, but we've never used them in battle against any foreign adversary.

00:00:39.794 --> 00:00:42.050
The men jumped out of the cars with these guns that I've never seen before.

00:00:42.050 --> 00:00:45.760
When they pulled the trigger, it was like a pulse.

00:00:48.592 --> 00:00:52.987
It was some kind of riot control that knocked you unconscious for a couple of minutes.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:01:02.080
They just pointed the thing in the direction they wanted it to go, and as soon as that beam hit that individual, it knocked them unconscious.

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.760
There was no running away.

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:21.759
It was on the Hummers and on the men; they would just go and scan the people as they were running, and people would just fall out like they're passing out.

00:01:24.062 --> 00:01:30.240
A new weapon that we've never seen before—nuclear weapons are a thing of the past.

00:01:31.577 --> 00:01:42.079
That may sound like, 'Boy, I don't know about that,' but I'm telling you all, technological advancements have surpassed nuclear energy.

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:49.520
I'm telling you, we're on the verge of a new industrial revolution.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:02:10.009
There are these new weapons and things we've never seen before that will become public, which they've been working on behind closed doors for probably decades.

00:02:10.009 --> 00:02:11.039
Who knows?

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:18.742
I saw new military technology that doesn't exist to the public yet—things that are top secret, I believe.

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:23.120
The Lord showed me things in military bases; the Lord showed me deep things.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:27.582
I saw time travel through portals and AI.

00:02:28.436 --> 00:02:31.680
I don't know how else to describe to y'all what I saw.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.640
It was so out there.

00:02:33.890 --> 00:02:47.768
I told my son, 'I'll do my best to draw you a picture of what I saw, but the only thing I can tell you is the movie Stargate.

00:02:47.768 --> 00:02:58.669
' That was some of the stuff I was looking at, and I thought, 'When is this happening?

00:02:58.669 --> 00:03:00.868
How did this happen?

00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:07.020
Is this further in the future?

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:15.359
' I don't know if this is something that's actually happening right now.

00:03:15.359 --> 00:03:27.260
So all of a sudden, near the Belarus area by Warsaw, Poland, I saw a humongous mushroom cloud kind of an explosion.

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:39.249
I said during this visitation when I was seeing all this in the spirit, 'Lord, oh no, they're going to use tactical nukes.

00:03:39.249 --> 00:03:50.640
' And the Lord said, 'No, this is a weapon that has never been used before, ever on the Earth.

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:52.080
We've never seen this.

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:59.062
' Everything within a 50-mile radius or bigger—the blast zone was huge—it vaporized everything.

00:03:59.062 --> 00:04:03.999
Everything disintegrated, but it didn't destroy the buildings.

00:04:11.315 --> 00:04:11.511
It was a wicked weapon.

00:04:15.828 --> 00:04:17.519
I saw an AI race and the Lord said, 'Because of the Biden administration, you're behind China.

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:33.040
' I saw China making new kinds of drones, but these were not drones in the sky; they were drones for the battlefield so they would not have to bring their soldiers out, so they would have drone wars.

00:04:42.116 --> 00:04:42.267
I saw a circle that looked like the alien from the movie Alien—the demonic movie from back then.

00:04:43.378 --> 00:04:45.680
It had the alien with the long, evil-looking face.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:59.074
I don't like to reference that, but it's the only thing I can say; I've seen the pictures of the alien head.

00:05:20.347 --> 00:05:20.893
That's what this drone looked like.

00:05:20.893 --> 00:05:22.629
They had.

00:05:22.629 --> 00:05:32.440
50-caliber guns with tracks and were using drone warfare for battle, and China was—there it is, the alien!

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:35.120
Do you see that?

00:05:40.510 --> 00:05:42.027
That's the way the shield looked on this drone.

00:05:42.027 --> 00:05:48.320
Now take it off; I don't want to look at it.

00:05:48.320 --> 00:06:05.131
I keep seeing these rooms with supercomputers—major computers—and the Lord said the information is coming to them so quickly through AI that they can't even translate it fast enough with a human mind.

00:06:05.131 --> 00:06:11.291
They can type in what they're wanting to know about.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:18.171
What we have with ChatGPT and Gemini is yesterday's stuff; it's no good.

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:32.424
The Lord said they have new technology so advanced that it's going to take AI to translate it for their minds to try to comprehend what the computer's saying.

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:39.013
AI will have to translate the AI; that's how advanced the technology has become.

00:06:39.013 --> 00:06:43.050
There are cures for cancer, diabetes, Alzheimer's, and dementia.

00:06:51.620 --> 00:06:51.880
People go, 'Well, yeah, it's Ivermectin.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:07:00.360
' No, it's something more than Ivermectin; this is something more advanced.

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:13.520
But the Lord said he was bringing forth new cures and new things that would go alongside the fact that people would trust AI in the days ahead.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:17.572
What did I tell you was behind AI?

00:07:17.572 --> 00:07:27.490
There was a massive demon embedded into the computers you're talking to that had digital writing, and the demon was taking over the AI with the moving digital code.

00:07:31.049 --> 00:07:37.459
It had horns on its head; I saw it.

00:07:41.200 --> 00:07:45.111
It was embedded into this mainframe of a major computer, but it was a dimension all in itself.

00:07:45.111 --> 00:07:51.991
AI is a dimension all in itself when it comes to the level of technological advancement that it is.

00:07:51.991 --> 00:07:52.986
It's endless.

00:07:54.106 --> 00:08:04.720
And the Lord showed me people putting in these codes through CERN and these demonic portals; you're talking to a demonic spirit.

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:12.226
That's why I try to warn you all: should you use AI, the Lord said, 'Harness it, Brandon; don't embrace it.

00:08:12.226 --> 00:08:19.644
' You'll not be able to get around not using it, for it is the future.

00:08:24.596 --> 00:08:24.773
I saw CERN sites being built all around the world.

00:08:24.773 --> 00:08:26.980
People were trying to copy what's happening in Switzerland.

00:08:26.980 --> 00:08:31.039
They were doing a massive one in China and I saw one in America.

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:34.080
But when they do this, something actually happens.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I saw a black portal that was created like Stargate.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
It was really thin, probably about three or four feet, and it looked like a black circle you could reach through as a dimension.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
You could see the black line like a donut around it, and inside it was alive—this black particle.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
It looked like some kind of demonic portal that they had created with the Hadron Collider.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
They were getting information from that black portal.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
It was very dark and demonic because it was like a black hole.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
You could stick your hand in it and go to the other side.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
Like I said, I don't understand all of it, but I'm telling you what I saw in this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
The Lord showed me them playing around with dark stuff.
